### GET /api/directors recupera todos los directores
GET http://localhost:3000/api/directors

### GET /api/directors/graph recupera datos de directores para hacer una grafica
GET http://localhost:3000/api/directors/graph

### GET /api/directors/:id recupera un director
GET http://localhost:3000/api/directors/1

### GET /api/directors/:id recupera un director - NOT FOUND(404)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/directors/50

### POST /api/directors/ crea un director 
POST http://localhost:3000/api/directors
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "John Ford",
    "birth_date" : "1880-12-12",
    "biography" : "Director muy bueno de peliculas del oeste",
    "photo_url" : "https://goldenglobes.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/01-john-ford.jpg?w=2000"
}

### PUT /api/directors/:id actualiza un director
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/directors/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "John Ford",
    "birth_date" : "1880-12-12",
    "biography" : "Director muy bueno de peliculas del oeste actualizado",
    "photo_url" : "https://goldenglobes.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/01-john-ford.jpg?w=2000"
}

### DELETE /api/directors/:id elimina un director
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/directors/1

### DELETE /api/directors/:id elimina un director - NOT FOUND(404)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/directors/50

